	(text "CHEMIN A — NEVE HERITAGE\n\nTopology: 3-transistor Class-A with global feedback\n\nQ1A (BC184C NPN): Common-emitter, Rc=R8A(10K), bias R6A/R7A(100K/100K)\nQ2A (BC214C PNP): Common-emitter, Re=R11A(7.5K), Rc=R12A(6.8K)\nQ3A (BD139 NPN):  Emitter-follower, R_biasA(390R/1W) to -24V\n\nFeedback: Q3A emitter → C6A(470µF) → SW1 Pole A (Rfb) → Q1A emitter\nGain ref: R9A = 47R (0.1%)\nMiller comp: C5A = 100pF NP0\n\nOutput: Q3A emitter → C_outA(220µF bipol + 4.7µF film) → R_serA(10R) → OUTPUT_A\n\nBias points (expected):\n  Vc1 ≈ +14V, Vb1 ≈ 0V, Ve1 ≈ -0.6V\n  Vc2 ≈ -10.5V\n  Vb3 = Vc2 ≈ -10.5V, Ve3 ≈ -11.2V\n  Ic3 = (Ve3+24)/390 ≈ 33mA"
		(at 25.4 25.4 0)
		(effects (font (size 1.524 1.524)) (justify left))
		(uuid "f4000001-nev-text-0004-000000000001")
	)
)
